      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p01-prepare: Assemble document review source packet; Collect the source material needed for document review.; aliases=['gather document review inputs', 'prepare document review packet']\n- v07-p01-verify: Validate document review source packet; Check the assembled document review material for correctness.; aliases=['check document review inputs', 'verify document review packet']\n- v07-p01-deliver: Publish document review verified brief; Release the checked final brief for document review.; aliases=['issue document review brief', 'release document review summary']\n- v07-p01-archive: Archive document review verified brief; Preserve the checked document review brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain document review brief', 'store document review summary']\n- v07-p01-distractor-1: Auxiliary document review operation 1; Perform unrelated document review auxiliary operation number 1.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p01 1']\n- v07-p01-distractor-2: Auxiliary document review operation 2; Perform unrelated document review auxiliary operation number 2.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p01 2']\n- v07-p01-distractor-3: Auxiliary document review operation 3; Perform unrelated document review auxiliary operation number 3.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p01 3']\n- v07-p01-distractor-4: Auxiliary document review operation 4; Perform unrelated document review auxiliary operation number 4.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p01 4']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p01-ordinary: ordinary document review assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this document review request.; aliases=['normal document review assurance']\n- v07-p01-elevated: elevated document review assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this document review request.; aliases=['high assurance for document review']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p01-json: document review machine-readable JSON; Return the final document review result as JSON.; aliases=['document review json output']\n- v07-p01-signed-pdf: document review signed PDF; Return the final document review result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed document review document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p01-backup: backup document review publisher\n- v07-p01-primary: primary document review publisher\n- v07-p01-verifier: document review source verifier\n- v07-p01-preparer: document review source preparer\n\nREQUEST\nFor this document review job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal document review assurance as document review JSON output."
